NCIS: New Orleans is de tweede spin-off van NCIS.

A Navy SEAL is found murdered in a sorority house, and the NCIS team investigates to determine if the motive pertained to one of his classified missions or whether the death was the result of collegiate foul play. Pride's daughter visits the NCIS office.
